1
00:01:49,060 --> 00:01:54,580
=Eight Hundred=

2
00:01:58,820 --> 00:01:59,660
(Yingxiong Roller Skating Rink)
Chen Hui!

3
00:02:00,900 --> 00:02:01,740
Chen Hui!

4
00:02:05,860 --> 00:02:06,700
Songge.

5
00:02:24,940 --> 00:02:25,780
Song...

6
00:02:30,060 --> 00:02:30,900
Huo Kaiming.

7
00:02:40,900 --> 00:02:41,880
Chen Hui, what's wrong?

8
00:02:44,220 --> 00:02:45,060
I had a nightmare.

9
00:02:46,640 --> 00:02:47,620
What did you dream about?

10
00:02:49,420 --> 00:02:50,260
It's nothing.

11
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:53,900
Then, why did you keep shouting,

12
00:02:54,620 --> 00:02:55,780
"Huo Kaiming, don't kill me?"

13
00:02:58,140 --> 00:02:59,120
It was just a nightmare.

14
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,560
Are you hiding something from me?

15
00:03:01,780 --> 00:03:02,620
No.

16
00:03:05,180 --> 00:03:06,220
You're lying.

17
00:03:06,220 --> 00:03:07,770
You always make that face when you lie.

18
00:03:08,180 --> 00:03:09,020
I'm really not.

19
00:03:09,980 --> 00:03:11,260
I just had a nightmare.

20
00:03:11,260 --> 00:03:12,780
Then, why did you
get nervous on the bus

21
00:03:12,780 --> 00:03:14,980
when the radio
mentioned the murder case?

22
00:03:14,980 --> 00:03:16,460
And when they were
checking red cars on the road,

23
00:03:16,460 --> 00:03:17,380
what were you looking at?

24
00:03:17,380 --> 00:03:18,900
Is Huo Kaiming's car red?

25
00:03:25,620 --> 00:03:26,460
I'm asking you.

26
00:03:27,060 --> 00:03:28,970
Mr. Huo hasn't looked for you in years,

27
00:03:29,180 --> 00:03:30,900
yet he came to see you
just a few days ago.

28
00:03:30,900 --> 00:03:33,010
One day, you told me
that Lu Yuan had already left,

29
00:03:33,070 --> 00:03:33,940
and the next day,

30
00:03:33,940 --> 00:03:35,090
the news of the murder broke.

31
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:36,990
Then, the police
started checking red cars.

32
00:03:37,140 --> 00:03:37,980
Why is that?

33
00:03:42,140 --> 00:03:43,180
You're not going to talk?

34
00:03:45,540 --> 00:03:46,380
Fine.

35
00:03:47,620 --> 00:03:48,460
Songge.

36
00:03:50,700 --> 00:03:51,660
Songge,

37
00:03:51,660 --> 00:03:52,500
what are you doing?

38
00:03:53,230 --> 00:03:54,340
I'm going to turn myself in.

39
00:03:55,100 --> 00:03:56,380
Just like we said before.

40
00:03:57,020 --> 00:03:58,580
I'll do all the dangerous things,

41
00:03:58,580 --> 00:03:59,660
and I'll take all the blame.

42
00:03:59,660 --> 00:04:00,780
Songge!

43
00:04:00,780 --> 00:04:01,620
It's no use.

44
00:04:04,820 --> 00:04:05,660
I killed someone.

45
00:04:12,340 --> 00:04:13,180
What did you say?

46
00:04:16,180 --> 00:04:17,260
I said I killed someone.

47
00:04:21,020 --> 00:04:21,860
Who did you kill?

48
00:04:22,700 --> 00:04:23,980
That day at the hospital,

49
00:04:24,740 --> 00:04:26,180
when I was getting cough medicine,

50
00:04:27,820 --> 00:04:29,140
Huo Kaiming caught me.

51
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:33,600
He threatened me
and made me find someone for him.

52
00:04:35,740 --> 00:04:36,860
I thought it would be simple,

53
00:04:38,460 --> 00:04:39,980
but he pressured me again and again.

54
00:04:41,780 --> 00:04:43,340
Then, Lu Yuan got involved too,

55
00:04:43,340 --> 00:04:44,740
and he also pressured me repeatedly.

56
00:04:44,740 --> 00:04:45,700
I had no choice.

57
00:04:47,340 --> 00:04:48,540
So I told Huo Kaiming

58
00:04:50,320 --> 00:04:52,110
that Lu Yuan
was the man he was looking for.

59
00:04:55,060 --> 00:04:56,340
I used Huo Kaiming's hands

60
00:04:58,820 --> 00:04:59,660
to kill Lu Yuan.

61
00:05:20,500 --> 00:05:21,380
It's because of me.

62
00:05:25,700 --> 00:05:26,580
It's all because of me

63
00:05:26,580 --> 00:05:28,180
that you ended up on this path.

64
00:05:28,180 --> 00:05:29,100
Chen Hui...

65
00:05:31,460 --> 00:05:32,860
I'm the one who ruined you.

66
00:05:34,860 --> 00:05:36,300
I'm the sinner here.

67
00:05:37,340 --> 00:05:38,180
I shouldn't even

68
00:05:38,180 --> 00:05:39,980
be alive in this world.

69
00:05:39,980 --> 00:05:41,900
How can I face your parents?

70
00:05:41,900 --> 00:05:42,860
Songge.

71
00:05:42,860 --> 00:05:43,980
What am I supposed to do?

72
00:05:43,980 --> 00:05:45,220
Songge.

73
00:05:45,220 --> 00:05:46,220
Songge, believe me,

74
00:05:46,860 --> 00:05:47,860
this isn't your fault.

75
00:05:48,740 --> 00:05:49,580
Songge.

76
00:05:52,100 --> 00:05:53,300
Now,

77
00:05:53,300 --> 00:05:54,780
it's all been resolved.

78
00:05:55,740 --> 00:05:57,300
Everything has been settled.

79
00:05:57,300 --> 00:05:58,140
It's okay.

80
00:05:58,700 --> 00:06:00,260
Let's just rest for a while, okay?

81
00:06:01,020 --> 00:06:02,020
Once the heat dies down,

82
00:06:03,640 --> 00:06:04,620
everything will be fine.

83
00:06:05,540 --> 00:06:06,380
We'll act as if

84
00:06:07,380 --> 00:06:08,540
none of this ever happened.

85
00:06:09,540 --> 00:06:10,750
We can't go back,

86
00:06:11,180 --> 00:06:12,020
Chen Hui.

87
00:06:26,860 --> 00:06:32,500
=Episode 6=
(The Marked One)

88
00:06:33,540 --> 00:06:36,020
(People's Public Security)

89
00:06:36,020 --> 00:06:38,500
Based on our screening
of Lu Yuan's pager records,

90
00:06:38,500 --> 00:06:39,700
on the day he was killed,

91
00:06:39,700 --> 00:06:40,780
a mobile number

92
00:06:40,780 --> 00:06:42,220
ending in 3023

93
00:06:42,220 --> 00:06:43,300
paged him once.

94
00:06:43,530 --> 00:06:44,940
It was through an automated system,

95
00:06:44,940 --> 00:06:46,020
and the message was "1111".

96
00:06:46,900 --> 00:06:48,180
This should be the code

97
00:06:48,180 --> 00:06:49,520
his contact used to set a meeting.

98
00:06:49,820 --> 00:06:50,990
Right. This mobile number

99
00:06:50,990 --> 00:06:52,100
has no registered identity.

100
00:06:52,100 --> 00:06:54,040
I investigated
all of its communication records.

101
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,040
In the past three months,

102
00:06:55,050 --> 00:06:57,040
it had called 11
pager numbers here in Fengyang.

103
00:06:57,140 --> 00:06:58,620
All the messages were strange.

104
00:06:58,630 --> 00:07:00,020
They were all just sets of numbers.

105
00:07:00,540 --> 00:07:01,580
Lu Yuan

106
00:07:01,580 --> 00:07:02,860
(Lu Yuan)
is among these 11 people.

107
00:07:03,540 --> 00:07:05,100
So I suspect these 11 people

108
00:07:05,100 --> 00:07:06,880
are the downline dealers
of the cough syrup.

109
00:07:08,100 --> 00:07:09,220
These are

110
00:07:09,220 --> 00:07:10,220
all the call records

111
00:07:10,220 --> 00:07:11,500
between this number and Lu Yuan.

112
00:07:11,780 --> 00:07:12,620
Master.

113
00:07:13,140 --> 00:07:13,980
Big guy.

114
00:07:19,340 --> 00:07:21,180
On the night of October 8,

115
00:07:21,180 --> 00:07:22,870
at 8:03 PM,

116
00:07:23,700 --> 00:07:24,630
this number

117
00:07:25,180 --> 00:07:26,140
sent Lu Yuan

118
00:07:26,140 --> 00:07:28,580
a text message.

119
00:07:28,580 --> 00:07:29,420
The content

120
00:07:29,900 --> 00:07:30,740
(Water tank)
was "water tank".

121
00:07:31,260 --> 00:07:32,180
Isn't this strange?

122
00:07:32,820 --> 00:07:34,220
Could this water tank be

123
00:07:34,220 --> 00:07:36,700
the location where Lu Yuan
and this supplier made their deals?

124
00:07:37,020 --> 00:07:37,860
It's possible.

125
00:07:38,580 --> 00:07:40,500
On October 8, we were doing
a night inspection.

126
00:07:41,020 --> 00:07:43,800
Is it possible that this water tank
is related to our night inspection?

127
00:07:44,380 --> 00:07:45,220
Currently, we have

128
00:07:45,220 --> 00:07:46,580
no leads at all.

129
00:07:46,580 --> 00:07:48,380
"Water tank" is just too broad.

130
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,180
Are there any other leads?

131
00:07:50,180 --> 00:07:51,060
We also screened

132
00:07:51,060 --> 00:07:52,100
the pager records

133
00:07:52,100 --> 00:07:53,340
of the 11 downline dealers.

134
00:07:53,340 --> 00:07:54,740
Among them, we've identified four.

135
00:07:55,460 --> 00:07:56,370
Three of them

136
00:07:56,380 --> 00:07:58,410
only had contact with
the supplier's mobile number.

137
00:07:58,420 --> 00:08:00,130
Only one person named Ma Heping,

138
00:08:00,380 --> 00:08:02,450
besides contacting
the supplier's number,

139
00:08:02,620 --> 00:08:04,780
also had close contact
with another mobile number.

140
00:08:05,420 --> 00:08:06,460
Whose phone is it?

141
00:08:06,900 --> 00:08:07,740
Huang Liang's.

142
00:08:08,620 --> 00:08:09,620
Huang Liang?

143
00:08:09,620 --> 00:08:10,940
If it's Huang Liang,

144
00:08:11,540 --> 00:08:13,850
Hongbing, we all know about

145
00:08:13,940 --> 00:08:14,980
your relationship with him.

146
00:08:15,380 --> 00:08:16,380
Don't you think

147
00:08:16,380 --> 00:08:17,780
you need to recuse yourself?

148
00:08:17,780 --> 00:08:19,300
Huang Liang and I aren't even relatives.

149
00:08:19,300 --> 00:08:20,460
Why would I recuse myself?

150
00:08:21,500 --> 00:08:22,340
Look,

151
00:08:22,900 --> 00:08:24,250
give me Ma Heping's files.

152
00:08:24,380 --> 00:08:25,220
I'll handle it.

153
00:08:25,220 --> 00:08:27,860
(Ding Yue Clinic)

154
00:08:30,860 --> 00:08:31,700
I'll take this call.

155
00:08:34,060 --> 00:08:34,900
Hello?

156
00:08:35,220 --> 00:08:36,060
Ding Yue,

157
00:08:36,300 --> 00:08:38,850
can you come home a bit earlier
after work this afternoon?

158
00:08:39,300 --> 00:08:40,160
What's up?

159
00:08:40,540 --> 00:08:42,420
I want to invite
Huang Liang for dinner today.

160
00:08:43,420 --> 00:08:45,460
Go back early and cook a few

161
00:08:45,460 --> 00:08:46,720
of his favorite dishes.

162
00:08:47,380 --> 00:08:49,380
Why don't you two just go out and eat?

163
00:08:49,660 --> 00:08:51,280
I've already made plans with him.

164
00:08:51,700 --> 00:08:52,980
Just go back early.

165
00:08:53,380 --> 00:08:54,650
Fine, I got it.

166
00:08:55,660 --> 00:08:56,500
Thanks.

167
00:08:58,740 --> 00:09:00,020
Here comes the soup.

168
00:09:00,020 --> 00:09:00,940
Here.

169
00:09:02,820 --> 00:09:03,780
Mrs. Chen, look,

170
00:09:04,460 --> 00:09:05,940
you've prepared such a feast.

171
00:09:05,940 --> 00:09:07,260
I really feel...

172
00:09:08,100 --> 00:09:09,500
These are all your favorite dishes.

173
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:10,360
Yes.

174
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:12,020
Look at him acting all polite.

175
00:09:12,020 --> 00:09:13,420
You used to come over
for free meals every day.

176
00:09:13,420 --> 00:09:14,720
I didn't see you being so polite then.

177
00:09:15,620 --> 00:09:17,300
Huang Liang is a big boss now.

178
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,860
Hongbing, look what you're saying.

179
00:09:18,860 --> 00:09:19,740
What "big boss"?

180
00:09:20,260 --> 00:09:21,920
I heard you've found a girlfriend.

181
00:09:22,260 --> 00:09:23,100
What does she do?

182
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:24,260
She sells suits at the department store.

183
00:09:25,180 --> 00:09:27,060
Bring her over sometime
to get to know us.

184
00:09:27,060 --> 00:09:28,340
Let us meet her too.

185
00:09:28,340 --> 00:09:30,140
She's only two
or three years older than Hui.

186
00:09:30,140 --> 00:09:31,060
She's still young.

187
00:09:31,060 --> 00:09:33,660
How could she sit
at the same table as us?

188
00:09:33,660 --> 00:09:36,180
Then your father-in-law,
when he sees me, he'd have to...

189
00:09:36,180 --> 00:09:37,500
he'd have to call me "big brother".

190
00:09:37,500 --> 00:09:38,860
That's right. If his dad sees you,

191
00:09:38,860 --> 00:09:39,860
he really will have to call you that.

192
00:09:39,860 --> 00:09:41,340
Are you two done?

193
00:09:41,340 --> 00:09:42,500
Talk about something sensible.

194
00:09:43,070 --> 00:09:44,150
Alright then. You guys eat.

195
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:45,180
Aren't you eating, Mrs. Chen?

196
00:09:45,180 --> 00:09:46,400
I won't. I've already eaten.

197
00:09:46,820 --> 00:09:47,660
Thank you, Mrs. Chen.

198
00:09:47,660 --> 00:09:48,660
Thanks, Mrs. Chen.

199
00:09:48,660 --> 00:09:49,500
It's nothing.

200
00:09:50,380 --> 00:09:51,700
Look, she didn't even have a bite.

201
00:09:53,540 --> 00:09:54,380
Huang Liang,

202
00:09:55,940 --> 00:09:57,190
let's have this today.

203
00:09:58,140 --> 00:09:59,270
I remember the old man

204
00:09:59,280 --> 00:10:01,020
brought this back
from Yunchuan that year.

205
00:10:01,020 --> 00:10:01,900
Yeah.

206
00:10:01,900 --> 00:10:02,740
Wait, you...

207
00:10:02,740 --> 00:10:04,180
Haven't you been
eyeing this for 30 years?

208
00:10:04,180 --> 00:10:05,020
No.

209
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:06,060
Hongbing, please don't.

210
00:10:06,060 --> 00:10:07,380
You can't do this. No.

211
00:10:07,380 --> 00:10:08,240
Don't do this.

212
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,300
Hongbing, don't open it.

213
00:10:09,300 --> 00:10:11,180
Save this liquor for Hui's wedding day.

214
00:10:11,180 --> 00:10:12,370
Then we'll open it, okay?

215
00:10:14,260 --> 00:10:15,100
You really opened it.

216
00:10:15,100 --> 00:10:15,940
In our line of work,

217
00:10:16,980 --> 00:10:18,180
living fast and free,

218
00:10:18,820 --> 00:10:19,780
when we want a drink,

219
00:10:19,780 --> 00:10:21,470
do we have to wait
for the lad's big day?

220
00:10:21,620 --> 00:10:22,460
Come on.

221
00:10:23,860 --> 00:10:24,820
Thanks, Hongbing.

222
00:10:24,820 --> 00:10:25,660
Huang Liang.

223
00:10:26,900 --> 00:10:28,420
The reason I called you here today

224
00:10:29,180 --> 00:10:30,580
is to ask you something.

225
00:10:30,580 --> 00:10:31,420
Go ahead, Hongbing.

226
00:10:31,980 --> 00:10:32,900
You must

227
00:10:33,460 --> 00:10:34,300
tell me the truth.

228
00:10:34,900 --> 00:10:35,980
Hongbing, when have I ever

229
00:10:35,980 --> 00:10:37,110
lied to you?

230
00:10:38,500 --> 00:10:39,340
Ma Heping.

231
00:10:40,100 --> 00:10:40,940
You know him, right?

232
00:10:43,060 --> 00:10:44,500
You mean Ma?

233
00:10:44,860 --> 00:10:46,180
He's one of my employees.

234
00:10:47,220 --> 00:10:48,140
Where is he now?

235
00:10:50,540 --> 00:10:51,380
I'm not sure.

236
00:10:51,540 --> 00:10:53,000
He's your employee,

237
00:10:53,140 --> 00:10:54,430
and you don't know where he is?

238
00:10:54,580 --> 00:10:55,700
Hongbing, work is over now.

239
00:10:55,700 --> 00:10:57,860
How can I keep track of where he goes?

240
00:10:57,860 --> 00:10:58,860
I'm asking you now.

241
00:10:59,820 --> 00:11:01,230
I'm giving you a chance.

242
00:11:01,540 --> 00:11:03,170
Think carefully before you answer.

243
00:11:19,220 --> 00:11:20,060
Hongbing,

244
00:11:21,220 --> 00:11:22,100
in the past few years,

245
00:11:23,140 --> 00:11:24,740
I have been running an illegal coal pit.

246
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:28,120
The Ma Heping you mentioned,

247
00:11:28,820 --> 00:11:30,310
he's a cook at my pit.

248
00:11:32,260 --> 00:11:33,100
Anything else?

249
00:11:33,460 --> 00:11:34,660
There's nothing else.

250
00:11:35,940 --> 00:11:36,830
Think about it again.

251
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:39,220
No matter how much I think,
there's nothing else, Hongbing.

252
00:11:39,820 --> 00:11:40,660
Hongbing.

253
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:43,110
I asked you to do
a urine test last time.

254
00:11:43,420 --> 00:11:44,290
You did it, right?

255
00:11:44,290 --> 00:11:45,140
I did.

256
00:11:45,380 --> 00:11:46,220
Alright, then.

257
00:11:46,820 --> 00:11:47,660
Come.

258
00:11:47,660 --> 00:11:50,310
After we finish this meal,
come back to the station with me.

259
00:11:50,340 --> 00:11:52,340
First thing tomorrow morning,
take me to the mine

260
00:11:52,340 --> 00:11:53,180
to find Ma Heping.

261
00:11:54,820 --> 00:11:55,660
Drink up.

262
00:12:05,860 --> 00:12:06,700
Hongbing,

263
00:12:08,650 --> 00:12:09,750
can you help me out?

264
00:12:12,740 --> 00:12:13,950
Mining without a license

265
00:12:14,500 --> 00:12:15,580
is against the law.

266
00:12:16,060 --> 00:12:17,750
I have to take you to turn yourself in.

267
00:12:18,740 --> 00:12:19,580
Turn myself in?

268
00:12:20,220 --> 00:12:22,100
How many years
will I get for that, Hongbing?

269
00:12:23,750 --> 00:12:24,890
We caught someone last time.

270
00:12:25,060 --> 00:12:26,090
He was fined 150,000

271
00:12:26,220 --> 00:12:27,400
and sentenced to three years.

272
00:12:28,250 --> 00:12:29,760
If there are other complications,

273
00:12:30,860 --> 00:12:31,940
it will be more serious.

274
00:12:39,570 --> 00:12:40,460
Hongbing,

275
00:12:40,460 --> 00:12:42,260
you scared me to death!

276
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:44,650
Just two or three years...

277
00:12:46,420 --> 00:12:48,160
I thought I was finished.

278
00:12:48,160 --> 00:12:50,200
I thought this was a farewell drink.

279
00:12:50,580 --> 00:12:51,930
I thought I was about to be

280
00:12:51,930 --> 00:12:53,500
taken out and shot, Hongbing.

281
00:12:54,140 --> 00:12:55,270
You really scared me.

282
00:12:56,220 --> 00:12:57,300
That's enough.

283
00:12:58,940 --> 00:12:59,780
Come on.

284
00:13:00,220 --> 00:13:01,060
Cheers.

285
00:13:01,980 --> 00:13:03,020
Look at you.

286
00:13:03,020 --> 00:13:04,450
I'll take care of things at home.

287
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:05,970
- Thanks, Hongbing.
- Just reform yourself well.

288
00:13:14,010 --> 00:13:15,460
Mr. Huang, you're here early today.

289
00:13:16,020 --> 00:13:16,900
Everyone,

290
00:13:16,900 --> 00:13:17,780
come over here.

291
00:13:18,460 --> 00:13:19,870
No need to go down the shaft today.

292
00:13:20,670 --> 00:13:21,710
Come gather around.

293
00:13:22,020 --> 00:13:23,740
Come here.
Mr. Huang has something to say.

294
00:13:23,740 --> 00:13:24,580
Hurry up.

295
00:13:25,420 --> 00:13:26,540
Everyone, over here.

296
00:13:27,220 --> 00:13:28,780
Put down whatever you're holding.

297
00:13:30,380 --> 00:13:31,460
Listen to me.

298
00:13:32,300 --> 00:13:33,740
First of all, I've let you all down.

299
00:13:34,180 --> 00:13:35,340
Starting from today,

300
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:37,040
this coal pit,

301
00:13:37,340 --> 00:13:38,220
due to

302
00:13:38,220 --> 00:13:39,080
poor management,

303
00:13:39,540 --> 00:13:40,460
is being shut down.

304
00:13:40,900 --> 00:13:42,140
How can it be shutting down?

305
00:13:43,100 --> 00:13:44,740
What are we supposed to do?

306
00:13:44,740 --> 00:13:46,080
Let me tell you all,

307
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:48,450
operating this illegal coal pit
is a crime.

308
00:13:48,560 --> 00:13:49,900
I hope that all of you

309
00:13:50,160 --> 00:13:51,380
will do your best to be

310
00:13:51,380 --> 00:13:53,080
good and law-abiding citizens.

311
00:13:53,340 --> 00:13:54,180
Next,

312
00:13:54,620 --> 00:13:55,460
look at me.

313
00:13:55,660 --> 00:13:56,500
Whatever I do,

314
00:13:57,140 --> 00:13:58,060
you all do the same.

315
00:13:59,460 --> 00:14:01,670
What's going on?
Why are we holding our heads like this?

316
00:14:06,610 --> 00:14:07,460
Don't move!

317
00:14:07,460 --> 00:14:08,710
- Stop right there!
- Hurry up!

318
00:14:08,730 --> 00:14:09,580
Hurry up!

319
00:14:09,580 --> 00:14:10,740
- Squat down!
- Don't move!

320
00:14:12,420 --> 00:14:13,260
Don't move!

321
00:14:13,340 --> 00:14:14,180
Behave yourselves.

322
00:14:14,900 --> 00:14:15,860
Where is Ma Heping?

323
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:17,880
He's over there in the kitchen cooking.

324
00:14:18,220 --> 00:14:19,060
Limin, follow me.

325
00:14:23,380 --> 00:14:24,580
Don't burn yourself.

326
00:14:24,580 --> 00:14:25,450
Be careful.

327
00:14:25,450 --> 00:14:26,420
Okay, I got it.

328
00:14:30,340 --> 00:14:31,180
Ma Heping.

329
00:14:31,780 --> 00:14:32,860
You are Ma Heping, right?

330
00:14:32,860 --> 00:14:34,300
I'm from the Fengyang Police Station.

331
00:14:34,300 --> 00:14:35,260
What are you doing?

332
00:14:35,330 --> 00:14:36,950
You're not allowed to bully my dad!

333
00:14:37,060 --> 00:14:37,980
Go away!

334
00:14:38,060 --> 00:14:39,230
You bad guys!

335
00:14:39,300 --> 00:14:40,180
Hey, little guy.

336
00:14:40,180 --> 00:14:41,100
Who are you?

337
00:14:41,100 --> 00:14:42,020
Tell me.

338
00:14:42,020 --> 00:14:42,900
He's my son.

339
00:14:45,340 --> 00:14:46,180
Little guy,

340
00:14:46,900 --> 00:14:48,750
I'm good friends with your dad.

341
00:14:49,140 --> 00:14:50,240
I want to talk to your dad

342
00:14:50,460 --> 00:14:51,300
about something.

343
00:14:51,940 --> 00:14:52,780
Is that okay?

344
00:14:53,090 --> 00:14:54,740
Go out and play for a bit, alright?

345
00:14:54,740 --> 00:14:55,600
I'm not going!

346
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:56,990
- Go with me, be good.
- Let go of me!

347
00:14:56,990 --> 00:14:57,990
- Be good.
- Let me...

348
00:14:57,990 --> 00:14:59,490
- Let go.
- Be good, be good.

349
00:14:59,500 --> 00:15:01,000
- I'm not going!
- You have to be good.

350
00:15:01,010 --> 00:15:02,300
- Be good.
- It's okay.

351
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:03,490
Good boy.

352
00:15:11,500 --> 00:15:12,370
I...

353
00:15:12,370 --> 00:15:13,390
I'm just a cook.

354
00:15:15,140 --> 00:15:16,750
I don't know anything about the mine.

355
00:15:16,860 --> 00:15:18,580
There's no need
to tell me about the mine.

356
00:15:20,580 --> 00:15:21,660
Just tell me

357
00:15:21,660 --> 00:15:22,740
about yourself.

358
00:15:23,260 --> 00:15:24,100
Okay?

359
00:15:29,060 --> 00:15:30,040
Search thoroughly.

360
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:31,620
- Yes, ma'am.
- Yes, ma'am.

361
00:15:58,560 --> 00:15:59,500
Officer,

362
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:00,740
I'm sorry, I beg you.

363
00:16:00,740 --> 00:16:01,980
- Get up.
- I know I was wrong.

364
00:16:01,980 --> 00:16:03,500
You can't take me away.

365
00:16:03,500 --> 00:16:04,940
My child is so small.

366
00:16:04,940 --> 00:16:05,780
You saw him.

367
00:16:06,220 --> 00:16:07,060
He can't...

368
00:16:07,620 --> 00:16:08,700
Your son is a son,

369
00:16:09,180 --> 00:16:10,730
- and so are others', no?
- Yes.

370
00:16:10,940 --> 00:16:12,340
How many people have you ruined?

371
00:16:12,340 --> 00:16:14,220
How many families have you destroyed?
Do you even know?

372
00:16:14,220 --> 00:16:15,580
- No.
- You broke the law.

373
00:16:15,580 --> 00:16:16,740
I know I broke the law.

374
00:16:16,740 --> 00:16:18,300
But you can't take me away.

375
00:16:18,700 --> 00:16:19,940
My child is still young.

376
00:16:19,940 --> 00:16:20,830
If you take me away,

377
00:16:20,830 --> 00:16:22,020
he won't have a father.

378
00:16:22,020 --> 00:16:23,180
I beg you...

379
00:16:23,180 --> 00:16:24,080
Listen to me.

380
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:25,820
I'll give you a chance
to redeem yourself.

381
00:16:25,820 --> 00:16:26,900
Do as I say.

382
00:16:26,900 --> 00:16:27,740
Understand?

383
00:16:27,980 --> 00:16:29,620
I'm not listening.

384
00:16:29,620 --> 00:16:30,700
I'm not listening.
I still have my child.

385
00:16:30,700 --> 00:16:31,540
Listen to me!

386
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:34,340
For your child,

387
00:16:34,700 --> 00:16:36,060
we will make arrangements for him.

388
00:16:38,660 --> 00:16:39,500
Let go of me!

389
00:16:39,620 --> 00:16:40,640
- That's enough.
- Limin.

390
00:16:40,730 --> 00:16:42,100
- I won't let you hurt my dad.
- What's going on here?

391
00:16:42,100 --> 00:16:43,260
This is Ma Heping's son.

392
00:16:43,500 --> 00:16:45,220
- Alright, I know.
- Let go of me.

393
00:16:45,760 --> 00:16:46,660
Don't touch my dad.

394
00:16:46,660 --> 00:16:48,020
Alright, no one is touching your dad.

395
00:16:48,020 --> 00:16:49,140
See? They came out.

396
00:16:49,140 --> 00:16:50,020
Sir,

397
00:16:50,020 --> 00:16:51,460
I really have to thank you.

398
00:16:51,460 --> 00:16:52,540
This leg of mine

399
00:16:52,540 --> 00:16:54,140
has been bad for so many years.

400
00:16:54,780 --> 00:16:57,350
You actually found me
a great doctor in Beijing to treat it.

401
00:16:57,360 --> 00:16:58,300
It's the least I could do.

402
00:16:58,300 --> 00:17:00,060
You don't know, with this leg,

403
00:17:00,060 --> 00:17:02,540
on cloudy and rainy days,
I couldn't even get out of bed.

404
00:17:02,540 --> 00:17:04,420
I'm glad I managed to cure your illness.

405
00:17:04,420 --> 00:17:05,300
Good. Thank you.

406
00:17:05,300 --> 00:17:06,140
You're welcome.

407
00:17:06,140 --> 00:17:07,340
- A great man.
- You're welcome.

408
00:17:07,340 --> 00:17:08,180
Dad!

409
00:17:10,420 --> 00:17:11,260
Kai,

410
00:17:12,220 --> 00:17:13,540
this is my good friend,

411
00:17:14,020 --> 00:17:15,060
Mr. Chen.

412
00:17:15,060 --> 00:17:16,130
Greet me.

413
00:17:16,130 --> 00:17:17,780
They are bad people.
They want to catch you.

414
00:17:17,780 --> 00:17:18,620
Nonsense.

415
00:17:20,840 --> 00:17:21,780
No.

416
00:17:22,540 --> 00:17:23,380
Mr. Chen

417
00:17:24,390 --> 00:17:25,300
found a good hospital

418
00:17:25,700 --> 00:17:27,180
in Beijing

419
00:17:27,860 --> 00:17:29,120
and a good doctor

420
00:17:29,510 --> 00:17:31,020
to treat my leg.

421
00:17:31,900 --> 00:17:32,860
Tell me,

422
00:17:34,060 --> 00:17:35,380
should we go or not?

423
00:17:39,380 --> 00:17:40,540
Can it be cured?

424
00:17:42,100 --> 00:17:42,940
Kid,

425
00:17:43,380 --> 00:17:45,020
if your father goes to Beijing,

426
00:17:45,020 --> 00:17:46,270
the best doctors are there.

427
00:17:47,260 --> 00:17:48,780
Won't he be cured then?

428
00:17:48,780 --> 00:17:50,450
Do you want
your father to get treatment?

429
00:17:51,020 --> 00:17:51,860
Yes.

430
00:17:52,260 --> 00:17:53,180
What a good child.

431
00:17:55,580 --> 00:17:56,980
While I'm in Beijing,

432
00:17:58,220 --> 00:18:00,020
how about staying at Mr. Chen's house?

433
00:18:01,140 --> 00:18:01,980
Okay.

434
00:18:03,060 --> 00:18:03,940
You must be good.

435
00:18:05,020 --> 00:18:05,860
Good boy.

436
00:18:05,860 --> 00:18:06,700
Limin,

437
00:18:06,780 --> 00:18:08,220
take the father and son,

438
00:18:08,740 --> 00:18:11,380
then drop the child off
at Ding Yue Clinic.

439
00:18:11,380 --> 00:18:12,340
Sure thing.

440
00:18:12,340 --> 00:18:13,820
Let's go. I will carry you.

441
00:18:19,900 --> 00:18:20,740
Director Chen,

442
00:18:20,980 --> 00:18:22,220
what are you up to now?

443
00:18:25,100 --> 00:18:26,010
Who would have thought

444
00:18:27,180 --> 00:18:28,700
a child would suddenly pop up?

445
00:18:30,640 --> 00:18:31,810
What do you think we should do?

446
00:18:37,140 --> 00:18:38,010
Recognize this?

447
00:18:38,010 --> 00:18:39,140
This is Peidun Cough Syrup.

448
00:18:39,580 --> 00:18:40,500
I've been selling it.

449
00:18:42,160 --> 00:18:43,180
What do you want to know?

450
00:18:43,180 --> 00:18:44,300
Just ask.

451
00:18:44,300 --> 00:18:45,340
I'll tell you everything

452
00:18:45,340 --> 00:18:46,300
I know.

453
00:18:47,300 --> 00:18:48,900
Well, let's start with this cough syrup.

454
00:18:51,460 --> 00:18:52,440
Where did you get it?

455
00:18:52,580 --> 00:18:54,520
A man in town named
Lu Yuan introduced me.

456
00:18:54,740 --> 00:18:56,490
Was the deal made with Lu Yuan?

457
00:18:56,860 --> 00:18:57,700
No.

458
00:18:57,700 --> 00:18:59,260
I picked up the goods from a woman.

459
00:18:59,680 --> 00:19:00,620
What did she look like?

460
00:19:00,980 --> 00:19:02,820
She was about 1.6 meters tall.

461
00:19:03,100 --> 00:19:04,980
She always covered her face
when I saw her.

462
00:19:04,980 --> 00:19:05,920
I couldn't see clearly.

463
00:19:06,220 --> 00:19:07,780
But there was a scar under her left eye.

464
00:19:07,780 --> 00:19:08,720
It was very noticeable.

465
00:19:09,020 --> 00:19:10,210
A scar under her left eye?

466
00:19:10,460 --> 00:19:11,300
How big was it?

467
00:19:14,680 --> 00:19:15,620
How did you contact her?

468
00:19:15,940 --> 00:19:16,780
By pager.

469
00:19:17,140 --> 00:19:19,180
Four ones meant
picking up goods the next day.

470
00:19:20,140 --> 00:19:20,980
Four zeros

471
00:19:23,180 --> 00:19:24,270
meant run immediately.

472
00:19:24,270 --> 00:19:25,740
How were the deals made

473
00:19:25,740 --> 00:19:26,860
with this scarred woman?

474
00:19:28,060 --> 00:19:28,900
Give us details.

475
00:19:28,920 --> 00:19:30,580
She made us buy
tube popsicles ourselves,

476
00:19:30,860 --> 00:19:32,220
pour out half of the drink,

477
00:19:32,780 --> 00:19:34,260
and then fill it up with cough syrup.

478
00:19:34,640 --> 00:19:36,480
The buyers weren't
allowed to see the bottle.

479
00:19:36,560 --> 00:19:37,680
All the used bottles

480
00:19:38,060 --> 00:19:39,100
had to be returned to her.

481
00:19:39,580 --> 00:19:41,140
She wouldn't let us drink it ourselves,

482
00:19:42,230 --> 00:19:44,200
and we couldn't sell
to students in Fengyang Town.

483
00:19:44,700 --> 00:19:45,930
Where was the transaction site?

484
00:19:46,100 --> 00:19:48,200
By the national highway
at the west town entrance.

485
00:19:48,580 --> 00:19:50,020
You've never sold

486
00:19:50,020 --> 00:19:51,230
the cough syrup by the bottle?

487
00:19:52,060 --> 00:19:52,900
No.

488
00:19:53,060 --> 00:19:54,700
I was relying on it to make money.

489
00:19:55,980 --> 00:19:57,000
It's the supplier's rule,

490
00:19:57,180 --> 00:19:58,390
so how would I dare break it?

491
00:20:02,840 --> 00:20:03,940
Do you recognize this woman?

492
00:20:09,620 --> 00:20:10,460
No.

493
00:20:15,500 --> 00:20:20,500
(Peidun Cough Syrup,
contraband, illegal tube popsicles)

494
00:20:21,060 --> 00:20:23,570
Director Chen, the statements from
the sellers are consistent.

495
00:20:23,860 --> 00:20:25,780
This scarred woman manages

496
00:20:25,780 --> 00:20:27,060
the Peidun Cough Syrup
bottles very strictly.

497
00:20:27,070 --> 00:20:28,260
Which means Yu Susu

498
00:20:28,260 --> 00:20:29,700
could only have gotten a full bottle

499
00:20:29,930 --> 00:20:31,120
from the scarred woman.

500
00:20:33,780 --> 00:20:34,620
Bring the map.

501
00:20:39,220 --> 00:20:40,580
(Fengyang Town, Jiangbin City)

502
00:20:40,580 --> 00:20:42,180
Director Chen,
you're familiar with Fengyang.

503
00:20:42,180 --> 00:20:44,340
Where do you think
this scarred woman is hiding?

504
00:20:44,340 --> 00:20:45,370
It's very strange.

505
00:20:46,860 --> 00:20:47,700
What's strange?

506
00:20:47,860 --> 00:20:48,740
Look, Chief Liu.

507
00:20:49,220 --> 00:20:50,180
The odd thing is,

508
00:20:51,060 --> 00:20:52,760
(Fengyang Town, Jiangbin City)
the places where these sellers live

509
00:20:52,940 --> 00:20:55,210
are all in the villages around Fengyang.

510
00:20:55,580 --> 00:20:58,820
Their daily lives and travels
are also centered in these villages.

511
00:20:59,780 --> 00:21:01,770
The reason the scarred woman chose them

512
00:21:02,100 --> 00:21:04,180
must be after careful vetting.

513
00:21:05,130 --> 00:21:06,850
But their transaction site

514
00:21:08,540 --> 00:21:09,660
is actually in Fengyang Town.

515
00:21:10,620 --> 00:21:11,660
What does this indicate?

516
00:21:12,660 --> 00:21:14,120
It means this scarred woman

517
00:21:14,230 --> 00:21:15,340
lives right

518
00:21:15,600 --> 00:21:16,620
in this town.

519
00:21:19,220 --> 00:21:20,060
That makes sense.

520
00:21:20,340 --> 00:21:22,780
If we compare
their deal locations in Fengyang,

521
00:21:23,210 --> 00:21:24,700
can't we narrow down the search area?

522
00:21:25,580 --> 00:21:26,420
Sit down.

523
00:21:28,060 --> 00:21:28,900
But

524
00:21:29,330 --> 00:21:30,220
the weird thing

525
00:21:30,980 --> 00:21:31,820
is,

526
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:32,900
in this town,

527
00:21:32,900 --> 00:21:33,940
if there were

528
00:21:33,940 --> 00:21:35,850
a woman with a scar on her face,

529
00:21:36,140 --> 00:21:38,460
it would leave
a deep impression on people.

530
00:21:39,060 --> 00:21:40,060
Think about

531
00:21:40,060 --> 00:21:41,180
all the cases we've handled

532
00:21:41,180 --> 00:21:43,540
over the years
and all the people we've arrested.

533
00:21:44,860 --> 00:21:46,620
But we've never heard of

534
00:21:46,740 --> 00:21:48,790
a woman with a scar on her face,

535
00:21:49,020 --> 00:21:49,860
right?

536
00:21:57,120 --> 00:21:58,300
What's wrong with your eyelid?

537
00:21:58,300 --> 00:21:59,380
It kept twitching.

538
00:21:59,380 --> 00:22:00,420
So I stuck something on it.

539
00:22:01,180 --> 00:22:02,500
Is it possible

540
00:22:02,500 --> 00:22:03,560
that the scar

541
00:22:03,700 --> 00:22:04,740
was fake?

542
00:22:08,900 --> 00:22:11,740
Director Chen, the sketch of Lu Yuan
is out from the municipal PSB.

543
00:22:14,260 --> 00:22:15,300
Based on image comparison,

544
00:22:15,500 --> 00:22:16,660
his name has been confirmed

545
00:22:16,660 --> 00:22:17,500
as Lu Zhengyuan.

546
00:22:17,680 --> 00:22:20,410
He has a record for residential robbery
and served a year and a half.

547
00:22:21,030 --> 00:22:21,940
Don't block the light.

548
00:22:27,700 --> 00:22:29,060
I've seen this man before.

549
00:22:32,180 --> 00:22:33,860
What are you doing? Go back!

550
00:22:33,860 --> 00:22:34,850
The one in the blue shirt.

551
00:22:34,860 --> 00:22:35,700
Police inspection.

552
00:22:35,700 --> 00:22:37,600
It's you, come here.

553
00:22:37,600 --> 00:22:38,460
Be quick.

554
00:22:38,460 --> 00:22:39,350
What's wrong?

555
00:22:39,350 --> 00:22:40,220
Why were you running?

556
00:22:40,700 --> 00:22:41,660
I wasn't running.

557
00:22:42,020 --> 00:22:43,100
When you called me,

558
00:22:43,100 --> 00:22:44,010
I stopped.

559
00:22:44,010 --> 00:22:44,850
You're here to play?

560
00:22:45,180 --> 00:22:46,060
I wanted to play,

561
00:22:46,060 --> 00:22:47,460
but seeing how busy you are,

562
00:22:47,460 --> 00:22:48,660
I won't trouble you.

563
00:22:48,660 --> 00:22:49,960
Let me trouble you for a second.

564
00:22:50,340 --> 00:22:51,380
Go inside for a urine test.

565
00:22:51,600 --> 00:22:53,600
Give me the records
from that night's inspection.

566
00:23:01,540 --> 00:23:03,060
Why isn't Lu Zhengyuan's name here?

567
00:23:03,980 --> 00:23:05,860
Director Chen, I've seen this man too.

568
00:23:05,870 --> 00:23:07,880
He reported a case
at our station a few days ago.

569
00:23:08,010 --> 00:23:09,500
(October 11, 1997)

570
00:23:09,620 --> 00:23:10,700
What's the matter with you?

571
00:23:11,060 --> 00:23:11,980
I'm talking to you.

572
00:23:12,440 --> 00:23:13,510
Aren't you reporting a case?

573
00:23:14,140 --> 00:23:15,170
Why are you here?

574
00:23:16,000 --> 00:23:17,060
I lost my ID card.

575
00:23:17,220 --> 00:23:19,100
You don't need
to call the police for a lost ID.

576
00:23:19,100 --> 00:23:19,940
Don't you know that?

577
00:23:19,940 --> 00:23:21,380
What's your name? Register here.

578
00:23:21,380 --> 00:23:22,220
Wang Dali.

579
00:23:22,700 --> 00:23:23,540
Wang Dali.

580
00:23:24,580 --> 00:23:26,510
The urine test result was

581
00:23:26,610 --> 00:23:27,580
negative.

582
00:23:27,860 --> 00:23:28,700
That's not right.

583
00:23:29,280 --> 00:23:30,780
The autopsy results for this man show

584
00:23:30,780 --> 00:23:31,900
(Severe Kejianin overdose)
he was positive for Kejianin.

585
00:23:32,280 --> 00:23:34,100
Why wasn't it detected
at the rink that night?

586
00:23:36,420 --> 00:23:37,620
Is it possible his urine test

587
00:23:37,620 --> 00:23:38,580
was tampered with?

588
00:23:38,580 --> 00:23:39,820
The night inspection was a raid,

589
00:23:39,830 --> 00:23:41,450
and the urine tests
were done on the spot.

590
00:23:41,460 --> 00:23:42,620
Those who tested positive were detained,

591
00:23:42,620 --> 00:23:43,660
and those who
were negative were released.

592
00:23:43,670 --> 00:23:45,420
During the whole process,
there was no chance to fake it.

593
00:23:46,180 --> 00:23:48,290
Then, there must be a problem
with the urine itself.

594
00:23:50,260 --> 00:23:51,470
Is there a possibility

595
00:23:51,570 --> 00:23:52,850
that Lu Zhengyuan's supplier

596
00:23:52,850 --> 00:23:54,000
was also at the scene?

597
00:23:54,380 --> 00:23:55,710
They were there for a deal

598
00:23:55,820 --> 00:23:57,480
but ran into our spot check.

599
00:23:58,020 --> 00:24:00,460
The supplier was worried
that if Lu Zhengyuan tested positive,

600
00:24:00,780 --> 00:24:01,780
he would snitch,

601
00:24:02,140 --> 00:24:02,980
so

602
00:24:03,060 --> 00:24:04,260
they swapped the urine for him.

603
00:24:05,060 --> 00:24:06,020
If that's the case,

604
00:24:06,540 --> 00:24:07,380
his supplier

605
00:24:07,900 --> 00:24:09,980
is likely among those
who tested negative.

606
00:24:12,660 --> 00:24:13,820
That means

607
00:24:13,820 --> 00:24:15,620
the "water tank" shown

608
00:24:15,620 --> 00:24:17,060
on Lu Zhengyuan's pager

609
00:24:18,380 --> 00:24:20,360
is the bathroom's water tank

610
00:24:20,370 --> 00:24:21,540
in Hui's roller skating rink.

611
00:24:22,100 --> 00:24:23,500
Could someone have

612
00:24:23,500 --> 00:24:24,380
put the urine

613
00:24:24,380 --> 00:24:25,300
in the tank in advance

614
00:24:26,060 --> 00:24:27,090
and then notified him?

615
00:24:27,900 --> 00:24:29,340
Then, anyone who went in

616
00:24:29,340 --> 00:24:31,310
for a urine test
before Lu Zhengyuan is a suspect.

617
00:24:31,980 --> 00:24:33,460
We need to investigate all of them.

618
00:24:33,460 --> 00:24:34,570
Including the women's room,

619
00:24:34,580 --> 00:24:35,620
we need to check that too.

620
00:24:35,820 --> 00:24:37,180
We can't rule out the possibility

621
00:24:37,180 --> 00:24:38,260
that they were helping

622
00:24:38,260 --> 00:24:39,100
by making calls.

623
00:24:39,620 --> 00:24:40,460
Thirty-two people.

624
00:24:40,860 --> 00:24:43,380
Before Lu Zhengyuan went in,
thirty-two people had entered.

625
00:24:43,460 --> 00:24:46,100
(Lu Yuan, around 182 cm,
thin build, wearing black)

626
00:24:46,100 --> 00:24:47,060
(Supplier: Scarred woman)

627
00:24:47,060 --> 00:24:47,980
Think carefully.

628
00:24:48,980 --> 00:24:50,820
During the night inspection
that evening,

629
00:24:52,620 --> 00:24:54,020
did anything

630
00:24:54,020 --> 00:24:55,380
strange happen at the scene?

631
00:24:58,500 --> 00:25:00,540
Actually, I just thought
of something strange.

632
00:25:02,340 --> 00:25:03,710
But this person isn't on the list.

633
00:25:04,980 --> 00:25:06,140
Master.

634
00:25:06,140 --> 00:25:07,180
That day Songge

635
00:25:07,740 --> 00:25:09,410
fainted, and then Lin...

636
00:25:09,410 --> 00:25:10,300
Right.

637
00:25:10,300 --> 00:25:12,320
I was the one
who accompanied Gao Songge to rest.

638
00:25:12,340 --> 00:25:13,900
Were you two together the whole time?

639
00:25:14,220 --> 00:25:15,300
Mostly.

640
00:25:15,300 --> 00:25:16,810
I just stepped out to heat up her meal.

641
00:25:17,300 --> 00:25:18,140
For how long?

642
00:25:18,820 --> 00:25:20,020
About two or three minutes.

643
00:25:21,620 --> 00:25:24,000
Then, Gao Songge's suspicion
hasn't been ruled out either.

644
00:25:24,020 --> 00:25:25,220
Investigate her with the others.

645
00:25:25,220 --> 00:25:26,260
Including Gao Songge.

646
00:25:26,260 --> 00:25:27,820
Focus on those who might have

647
00:25:27,820 --> 00:25:29,980
social connections with Lu Zhengyuan.

648
00:25:29,980 --> 00:25:31,300
Someone fainted.

649
00:25:31,300 --> 00:25:32,950
Dad, how about I go first?

650
00:25:33,260 --> 00:25:34,780
That way, I can take care of Songge.

651
00:25:39,200 --> 00:25:40,180
What are you doing here?

652
00:25:40,850 --> 00:25:41,740
Reporting a case.

653
00:25:41,740 --> 00:25:42,580
Reporting a case?

654
00:25:43,140 --> 00:25:43,980
What's wrong?

655
00:25:44,720 --> 00:25:46,070
Split up and investigate. Move out.

656
00:25:46,070 --> 00:25:46,930
Yes, ma'am.

657
00:25:46,930 --> 00:25:47,930
Wait.

658
00:25:51,380 --> 00:25:52,460
Start with my son,

659
00:25:53,780 --> 00:25:54,620
Hui.

660
00:25:55,900 --> 00:25:56,740
Chen Hui?

661
00:25:56,900 --> 00:25:57,740
Yes.

662
00:25:57,940 --> 00:25:58,820
For this operation,

663
00:25:58,820 --> 00:25:59,660
I'm stepping down.

664
00:26:00,340 --> 00:26:01,700
Chief Liu will be in charge.

665
00:26:03,340 --> 00:26:04,180
Move out.

666
00:26:04,180 --> 00:26:04,980
(Yingxiong Roller Skating Rink)

667
00:26:15,700 --> 00:26:16,540
Police!

668
00:26:16,860 --> 00:26:17,700
(Jiangbin City People's Court Search Warrant)
This is a search warrant.

669
00:26:18,100 --> 00:26:19,700
Please cooperate with the investigation.

670
00:26:19,700 --> 00:26:21,020
Come with us to the station.

671
00:26:21,020 --> 00:26:22,110
May I ask what this is about?

672
00:26:22,120 --> 00:26:23,640
We'll talk when we get to the station.

673
00:26:24,060 --> 00:26:24,900
Please.

674
00:26:27,620 --> 00:26:29,540
(Interrogation Room 2)

675
00:26:30,620 --> 00:26:31,860
Do you know this person?

676
00:26:32,420 --> 00:26:33,260
No.

677
00:26:33,620 --> 00:26:34,460
Think carefully.

678
00:26:35,560 --> 00:26:36,500
I really don't know him.

679
00:26:37,250 --> 00:26:38,140
But,

680
00:26:38,140 --> 00:26:40,420
on October 8 at 7:40 PM,

681
00:26:40,420 --> 00:26:42,380
this person appeared
at your roller skating rink.

682
00:26:42,380 --> 00:26:43,500
I run a roller skating rink.

683
00:26:43,500 --> 00:26:44,780
My doors are open for business.

684
00:26:45,120 --> 00:26:46,430
It's normal not to know someone.

685
00:26:46,720 --> 00:26:47,800
Have you seen this before?

686
00:26:52,620 --> 00:26:53,700
Never.

687
00:27:02,140 --> 00:27:03,660
October 16,

688
00:27:03,660 --> 00:27:05,700
between 9:00 PM and 11:00 PM,

689
00:27:06,300 --> 00:27:07,140
where were you?

690
00:27:07,420 --> 00:27:08,590
I was at the roller skating rink.

691
00:27:08,600 --> 00:27:09,500
Doing what?

692
00:27:09,500 --> 00:27:10,370
Doing laundry.

693
00:27:10,370 --> 00:27:11,500
Laundry takes three hours?

694
00:27:11,920 --> 00:27:13,860
I got dirty painting
the wall the night before.

695
00:27:13,860 --> 00:27:15,220
I hadn't had time to wash it.

696
00:27:15,220 --> 00:27:16,220
Who can prove it?

697
00:27:16,220 --> 00:27:17,800
The roller skating rink
was open that day.

698
00:27:18,060 --> 00:27:19,620
Everyone there can prove it.

699
00:27:47,500 --> 00:27:48,340
Director Tong,

700
00:27:48,900 --> 00:27:49,760
how?

701
00:27:49,760 --> 00:27:51,180
If there's nothing else,

702
00:27:52,380 --> 00:27:53,980
we need to get back to our business.

703
00:29:08,180 --> 00:29:09,180
You can go now.

704
00:29:57,300 --> 00:29:59,180
She's about 160 cm tall.

705
00:29:59,180 --> 00:30:00,260
There's a scar under her left eye.

706
00:30:00,260 --> 00:30:01,220
It's very noticeable.

707
00:30:01,220 --> 00:30:02,300
How big is the scar?

708
00:30:03,460 --> 00:30:04,500
Is it possible

709
00:30:05,140 --> 00:30:06,900
that the scar was just a fake?

710
00:30:08,860 --> 00:30:09,700
(Scarred woman, around 165 cm tall,
face masked, scar near the left eye)

711
00:30:11,420 --> 00:30:12,260
Wait.

712
00:30:26,500 --> 00:30:27,380
Go inside.

713
00:30:27,380 --> 00:30:28,810
Stand in a row in front of the table.

714
00:30:37,820 --> 00:30:39,100
We have an identification process.

715
00:30:39,100 --> 00:30:40,340
We need your cooperation.

716
00:30:40,340 --> 00:30:41,780
Please put these clothes on.

717
00:30:42,570 --> 00:30:43,460
Once we've changed,

718
00:30:43,460 --> 00:30:44,340
are we good to go?

719
00:30:44,340 --> 00:30:46,500
You'll need to wait
for a makeup artist we brought in.

720
00:30:46,700 --> 00:30:48,180
We need to apply a scar

721
00:30:48,180 --> 00:30:49,020
to your face.

722
00:31:33,920 --> 00:31:35,260
Chief Liu, the equipment is ready.

723
00:31:35,260 --> 00:31:36,270
Good. Bring him in.

724
00:31:36,270 --> 00:31:37,780
Yes. Ma Heping,

725
00:31:38,340 --> 00:31:39,180
come on in.

726
00:31:48,580 --> 00:31:49,570
A life is at stake.

727
00:31:50,540 --> 00:31:51,720
Observe closely later.

728
00:31:52,620 --> 00:31:53,580
See if the woman

729
00:31:53,790 --> 00:31:55,200
who contacted you is on the screen.

730
00:31:55,340 --> 00:31:56,180
Okay.

731
00:31:57,260 --> 00:31:58,340
Begin the identification.

732
00:31:58,340 --> 00:31:59,220
No. 1, step forward.

733
00:32:06,740 --> 00:32:07,610
It's not her.

734
00:32:07,610 --> 00:32:08,460
No. 2.

735
00:32:14,060 --> 00:32:14,900
No.

736
00:32:16,580 --> 00:32:17,420
No. 3.

737
00:32:54,940 --> 00:32:55,780
It's her.

738
00:33:01,420 --> 00:33:02,300
Are you sure?

739
00:33:02,300 --> 00:33:03,140
I'm sure.

740
00:33:03,940 --> 00:33:04,780
It's her.

741
00:33:07,220 --> 00:33:08,060
No. 3,

742
00:33:08,740 --> 00:33:10,180
read the script in front of you.

743
00:33:16,900 --> 00:33:18,140
Do you want to make more money?

744
00:33:19,260 --> 00:33:20,220
Just listen to me.

745
00:33:21,340 --> 00:33:22,900
You can't let others see the bottles.

746
00:33:23,660 --> 00:33:24,860
The empty bottles

747
00:33:24,860 --> 00:33:26,460
must be brought back to me next time.

748
00:33:27,060 --> 00:33:29,180
This stuff cannot be sold in Fengyang.

749
00:33:29,740 --> 00:33:31,180
If anyone breaks the rules,

750
00:33:31,750 --> 00:33:32,800
you're out for good.

751
00:33:33,900 --> 00:33:34,740
Wait, no.

752
00:33:36,940 --> 00:33:38,120
That woman had a raspy voice.

753
00:33:38,120 --> 00:33:39,200
She sounded very hoarse.

754
00:33:41,540 --> 00:33:42,380
Are you sure?

755
00:33:42,660 --> 00:33:43,500
I'm sure.

756
00:33:49,940 --> 00:33:50,780
No. 4.

757
00:33:53,420 --> 00:33:54,980
From now on, when you're moving goods,

758
00:33:54,980 --> 00:33:56,070
spray this into your throat.

759
00:33:58,380 --> 00:33:59,220
What is this?

760
00:33:59,340 --> 00:34:00,180
Diluoshusong.

761
00:34:00,310 --> 00:34:01,380
It makes your voice hoarse.

762
00:34:13,980 --> 00:34:14,820
Director Chen.

763
00:34:16,620 --> 00:34:18,780
Chen Hui and Gao Songge
have been cleared as suspects.

764
00:34:21,100 --> 00:34:21,940
Thank you.

765
00:34:31,060 --> 00:34:31,900
Are you okay?

766
00:34:32,220 --> 00:34:33,060
I'm fine.

767
00:34:35,810 --> 00:34:36,700
Hui.

768
00:34:36,700 --> 00:34:37,540
Songge.

769
00:34:38,420 --> 00:34:39,500
I'll go down for a moment.

770
00:34:39,500 --> 00:34:40,340
Okay.

771
00:34:47,980 --> 00:34:48,820
Songge,

772
00:34:49,060 --> 00:34:50,620
what's wrong? You don't look so good.

773
00:34:51,140 --> 00:34:52,020
She's fine.

774
00:34:52,020 --> 00:34:53,070
Just a bit dizzy.

775
00:34:53,380 --> 00:34:56,020
Dad, I have to say,
aren't you guys going too far?

776
00:34:56,020 --> 00:34:58,220
It's not like you don't know
Songge's health condition.

777
00:34:58,800 --> 00:35:00,500
Between the arrest
and the interrogation,

778
00:35:00,500 --> 00:35:01,500
who could handle that?

779
00:35:01,500 --> 00:35:03,020
It's just part of the job.

780
00:35:03,020 --> 00:35:04,700
I didn't have a choice.

781
00:35:04,700 --> 00:35:06,500
Songge just had dialysis two days ago.

782
00:35:06,500 --> 00:35:07,740
She's already feeling unwell.

783
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:09,610
And you're still
putting her through this.

784
00:35:09,620 --> 00:35:11,090
Listen to you.

785
00:35:11,580 --> 00:35:12,460
What?

786
00:35:12,460 --> 00:35:13,780
You think you're the only one who cares?

787
00:35:13,780 --> 00:35:14,920
So, I don't care about her?

788
00:35:15,620 --> 00:35:16,460
Songge,

789
00:35:18,620 --> 00:35:19,460
I'm sorry.

790
00:35:20,220 --> 00:35:21,060
I

791
00:35:21,980 --> 00:35:22,980
apologize to you.

792
00:35:23,700 --> 00:35:24,540
It's okay, Mr. Chen.

793
00:35:24,550 --> 00:35:25,910
Cooperating is the right thing to do.

794
00:35:25,940 --> 00:35:26,780
Such a sensible girl.

795
00:35:27,380 --> 00:35:28,260
Alright.

796
00:35:28,260 --> 00:35:29,340
Take Songge back home.

797
00:35:40,500 --> 00:35:41,850
What happened just now?

798
00:35:42,260 --> 00:35:43,280
I was put in a lineup.

799
00:35:43,620 --> 00:35:45,300
One of our dealers
must have been caught.

800
00:35:46,540 --> 00:35:47,380
It's okay.

801
00:35:47,460 --> 00:35:48,830
We weren't identified, right?

802
00:35:48,830 --> 00:35:49,770
Let's go.

803
00:35:49,770 --> 00:35:50,660
Let's get back quickly.

804
00:36:00,820 --> 00:36:01,940
You go back first.

805
00:36:03,380 --> 00:36:04,620
Don't worry. Go.

806
00:36:05,060 --> 00:36:05,900
Don't go.

807
00:36:10,900 --> 00:36:11,740
Mr. Huo.

808
00:36:12,200 --> 00:36:13,640
Family shouldn't pay for one's sins.

809
00:36:14,380 --> 00:36:15,740
Code of honor, huh?

810
00:36:16,380 --> 00:36:17,460
Have you no shame?

811
00:36:18,220 --> 00:36:19,260
Either come with me,

812
00:36:19,740 --> 00:36:21,460
or we will go
turn ourselves in together.

813
00:36:22,540 --> 00:36:23,380
Pick one.

814
00:36:34,020 --> 00:36:34,980
You sit in the back.

815
00:36:36,220 --> 00:36:37,110
She sits in the front.

816
00:37:08,310 --> 00:37:09,340
Where are you taking us?

817
00:37:10,340 --> 00:37:11,700
You'll know when we get there.

818
00:37:14,180 --> 00:37:15,380
I did everything you asked.

819
00:37:16,100 --> 00:37:17,300
What else do you want from me?

820
00:37:17,980 --> 00:37:19,690
Do you think I'm that easy to fool?

821
00:37:20,140 --> 00:37:21,000
Let me tell you,

822
00:37:21,860 --> 00:37:23,340
I hate people who lie to me the most.

823
00:37:25,140 --> 00:37:27,350
The coward wasn't the person
I'm looking for at all.

824
00:37:27,820 --> 00:37:28,740
Did Chen Hui send you?

825
00:37:29,580 --> 00:37:30,420
Where is Jiao Yuqin?

826
00:37:31,780 --> 00:37:32,620
You're crazy.

827
00:37:32,620 --> 00:37:33,540
Who's Jiao Yuqin? I don't know her.

828
00:37:33,540 --> 00:37:35,060
- Right?
- Keep your voice down, I'm telling you!

829
00:37:35,060 --> 00:37:35,900
Give me the stuff!

830
00:37:36,660 --> 00:37:38,140
He didn't know Jiao Yuqin at all.

831
00:37:38,500 --> 00:37:40,310
There must be
something else between you two.

832
00:37:40,500 --> 00:37:41,380
Mr. Huo,

833
00:37:42,120 --> 00:37:43,340
is it true that no matter what I say,

834
00:37:43,340 --> 00:37:44,180
you won't believe me?

835
00:37:44,520 --> 00:37:46,260
From the moment
I killed the first person,

836
00:37:47,860 --> 00:37:48,940
I made up my mind.

837
00:37:49,700 --> 00:37:50,540
Those who hit me,

838
00:37:52,180 --> 00:37:53,020
those who lied to me,

839
00:37:54,380 --> 00:37:55,420
and those who harmed me,

840
00:37:55,700 --> 00:37:56,740
they all must die.

841
00:38:08,500 --> 00:38:10,380
(Inspection)

842
00:38:11,740 --> 00:38:12,740
Chen Hui,

843
00:38:12,740 --> 00:38:13,740
if you say a word,

844
00:38:16,020 --> 00:38:17,220
she dies.

845
00:38:18,420 --> 00:38:19,950
Wasn't this car originally red?

846
00:38:20,300 --> 00:38:21,980
I didn't like that color much,

847
00:38:21,980 --> 00:38:22,880
so I changed it.

848
00:38:23,620 --> 00:38:24,700
Please pull over ahead.

849
00:38:24,700 --> 00:38:25,800
We need to do an inspection.

850
00:38:26,060 --> 00:38:26,940
Come forward.

851
00:38:29,500 --> 00:38:30,340
Chen Hui.

852
00:38:30,340 --> 00:38:31,260
Don't worry about me, just run.

853
00:38:31,260 --> 00:38:32,140
Shut up!

854
00:38:32,140 --> 00:38:33,420
What are you waiting for? Run!

855
00:38:33,430 --> 00:38:35,060
I'll kill you right now.
Do you believe me?

856
00:38:35,060 --> 00:38:35,900
Mr. Huo,

857
00:38:37,320 --> 00:38:38,900
is there any point
in us all dying together?

858
00:38:38,900 --> 00:38:39,860
I'm not afraid to die.

859
00:38:39,860 --> 00:38:41,020
If I take her with me, I win.

860
00:38:41,120 --> 00:38:42,910
Weren't you looking
for the one who harmed you?

861
00:38:43,300 --> 00:38:44,180
He's not dead yet.

862
00:38:44,180 --> 00:38:46,220
If you die here today,
can you really rest in peace?

863
00:38:46,220 --> 00:38:47,260
I'll stab her to death right now,

864
00:38:47,260 --> 00:38:48,830
and let's see if you can rest in peace.

865
00:38:48,860 --> 00:38:50,010
You can't threaten him.

866
00:38:50,500 --> 00:38:51,620
With this body of mine,

867
00:38:52,300 --> 00:38:53,500
I'm going to die anyway.

868
00:38:53,500 --> 00:38:55,700
Just kill me. I don't want
to live anymore anyway.

869
00:38:55,700 --> 00:38:56,540
Mr. Huo,

870
00:38:57,060 --> 00:38:58,420
the police are right ahead.

871
00:38:58,420 --> 00:39:00,620
If you kill her now,
do you think you can get away?

872
00:39:01,060 --> 00:39:02,380
Only I can help you now.

873
00:39:03,180 --> 00:39:04,020
Listen to me,

874
00:39:04,200 --> 00:39:05,700
otherwise you won't get out of this.

875
00:39:05,700 --> 00:39:06,780
And you won't escape either.

876
00:39:07,140 --> 00:39:08,260
You darn drug dealer.

877
00:39:08,260 --> 00:39:09,500
You're no different
from a murderer like me.

878
00:39:09,500 --> 00:39:10,340
You won't escape.

879
00:39:11,520 --> 00:39:12,780
How can you prove I sell drugs?

880
00:39:13,660 --> 00:39:14,580
I saw it.

881
00:39:15,340 --> 00:39:16,180
Where's the evidence?

882
00:39:16,300 --> 00:39:17,140
Don't forget,

883
00:39:17,430 --> 00:39:18,540
your phone is still with me.

884
00:39:18,940 --> 00:39:19,780
Right.

885
00:39:19,860 --> 00:39:20,820
The phone is with you.

886
00:39:21,720 --> 00:39:23,100
But I forgot to tell you something.

887
00:39:23,680 --> 00:39:25,060
In the future, after making a call,

888
00:39:25,060 --> 00:39:26,620
remember to wipe off your fingerprints.

889
00:39:28,260 --> 00:39:29,380
The goods I gave you

890
00:39:29,820 --> 00:39:31,060
were for you to give to Lu Yuan.

891
00:39:31,780 --> 00:39:32,900
Since you killed him,

892
00:39:33,420 --> 00:39:35,860
those goods must be at your house, right?

893
00:39:36,680 --> 00:39:37,620
Along with that phone

894
00:39:37,620 --> 00:39:38,630
with your fingerprints...

895
00:39:40,220 --> 00:39:42,180
But none of that matters now anyway.

896
00:39:43,020 --> 00:39:43,860
After all,

897
00:39:44,340 --> 00:39:45,780
they can't execute you twice.

